00:30:40.565 --> 00:30:47.305
in which a brother is to be chosen and you have to tie a, a little

00:30:47.525 --> 00:30:51.225
thread on the wrist of that person.

00:30:53.505 --> 00:30:59.045
We don't have this kind of a system in the West, Western societies.

00:31:00.465 --> 00:31:07.645
But when Alexander invaded our country, he was married to an Indian lady

00:31:09.305 --> 00:31:14.705
and as luck would have it, unfortunately, once he lost his battle

00:31:15.385 --> 00:31:20.505
and he was taken into prison and taken uh..

00:31:21.585 --> 00:31:28.505
into a dungeon, I should say, and made him stay there. This king called Puru

00:31:29.165 --> 00:31:35.425
wanted that somehow Alexander should not proceed any further in India to destroy it.

00:31:39.105 --> 00:31:44.305
Now, that was the day of this rakhi, full moon.

00:31:44.905 --> 00:31:47.905
His wife was a clever Indian lady

00:31:48.785 --> 00:31:55.265
so she sent a, that thread in one plate covered with a cloth - that's how we send it -

00:31:56.325 --> 00:32:02.765
to the king and the king asked, "All right, tie that to me."

00:32:03.305 --> 00:32:08.545
When they tied it, he said, "Who is my sister, who has sent for me?"

00:32:09.245 --> 00:32:12.345
They said, "It is Alexander's wife."

00:32:13.265 --> 00:32:19.945
"She has sent it to me, I've become her brother, Oh God!" He ran to the dungeon,

00:32:20.425 --> 00:32:28.085
he fell at the feet of Alexander, he said, "Sir, I'm sorry. Uh.. whatever I've done, please forgive me.

00:32:28.345 --> 00:32:34.305
You are welcome." He took him with him and he put him on his throne. He said, "Let me wash your feet,

00:32:34.605 --> 00:32:41.205
you are my sister's husband, I've done such a harm to you. God will never forgive me - you have to forgive me."

00:32:41.465 --> 00:32:49.425
This Alexander had no idea what had gone wrong with this king - he thought he's gone mad or what, what is he trying to do?

00:32:50.425 --> 00:32:58.385
So, then he gave lots of clothes and lots of ornaments for his sister and everything and he sent her back to his house.

00:33:00.945 --> 00:33:07.625
When he came home, his wife was smiling, he said, "What is this, this king has gone mad or what?

00:33:07.865 --> 00:33:13.805
He has left me alone and now if I conquer, I may win the whole of India."

00:33:14.605 --> 00:33:21.725
She said, "What did you do?" She said, "Nothing, I just sent a thread to him today." He said, "Thread,

00:33:22.325 --> 00:33:26.425
what was that thread?" She said, "Is a thread from a sister to a brother."

00:33:26.845 --> 00:33:33.665
"Oh God," he said, "For a thread he left me out, I'm such a dangerous person."

00:33:34.045 --> 00:33:39.265
He said, "These Indians with their symbols and their lives, I cannot manage them.

00:33:39.485 --> 00:33:45.425
Imagine, for a thread they leave out such an, such an enemy, like me." He said, "I'm not going to go further."

00:33:45.745 --> 00:33:49.385
And then he took a poet Chandravardai from

00:33:49.585 --> 00:33:54.285
Delhi and went back and he had tremendous respect for India.

