00:38:16.245 --> 00:38:23.885
There's no lust, there's no greed - all these stupid ideas that have come to us

00:38:24.145 --> 00:38:29.425
of homosexuality, this and that, these are all, all is lost.

00:38:31.445 --> 00:38:34.925
You just love the other person only for love sake.

00:38:37.105 --> 00:38:42.685
Pure love that manifests.

00:38:43.585 --> 00:38:50.285
You see the whole world as a drama - you witness it; watching everything that's happening.

00:38:52.165 --> 00:38:57.265
You're not worried, you're not upset. I'm never upset about the

00:38:57.605 --> 00:39:01.885
uh.. airport or going to the aeroplane - nothing of the kind -

00:39:03.745 --> 00:39:11.305
because I know the aeroplane has to wait for Me and I reach there, the aeroplane is there.

00:39:12.845 --> 00:39:19.565
