00:39:35.485 --> 00:39:41.905
Like the water - one wave rises falls off, another wave rises falls off, another wave rises falls off.

00:39:42.165 --> 00:39:46.305
We're on the cusp, cusp of every wave of our thoughts.

00:39:47.885 --> 00:39:51.625
But there's a little, very little space in between.

00:39:52.325 --> 00:39:57.065
One thought comes from the future or from the past goes to the past or past to the future

00:39:57.865 --> 00:40:01.065
and we're just dancing on top of those thoughts.

00:40:02.065 --> 00:40:07.185
When the Kundalini rises, these thoughts elongate and the space increases,

00:40:08.905 --> 00:40:14.025
then you become thoughtlessly aware - you're aware but you're thoughtless.

00:40:17.985 --> 00:40:23.425
